{"tid":763581,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"基督教父母拒絕協助同性戀兒子申請大學助學金 中學老師助眾籌學費兼超額完成","createTime":"2018-08-01T08:45:30.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-06T03:48:13.000Z","uid":136994,"like":204,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":38,"replies":[{"pid":"0900d108afd5275d9602fd867c92dfea40ca2df5","tid":763581,"uid":136994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-01T08:45:30.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180801/s00005/1533094339071\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180801%2Fs00005%2F1533094339071&d=LDTxD5OmsASDaJfIw5fsuv1gJfeR7%2BEkjjir5NquRfg%3D&h=b4dec999\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180801%2Fs00005%2F1533094339071&h=1a715231\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180801/s00005/1533094339071</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20180801/s00005/833aa51e959ca76259d80d33ba5f53a1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20180801%2Fs00005%2F833aa51e959ca76259d80d33ba5f53a1.jpg&h=cfcf8596&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n美國佛羅里達州一名高中畢業生，因其同性戀傾向而在信奉基督的父母反對下，無法申請助學金，一度令他就讀心儀大學的機會渺茫。這名青年其後獲以前的生物科老師協助，並在網上眾籌，截至本港時間周三（1日）早上11時許，已籌得近6.5萬美元（約50.8萬港元），是他首學年所需學費的3倍多。<br />\n<br />\n18歲的歐文（Seth Owen）是校內名列前矛的學生，亦是畢業生代表。他表示，基督徒的父母發現他是同志後，即安排他接受輔導及「修正治療」(conversion therapy)。<br />\n<br />\n歐文日前以校內成績平均積點（GPA）4.16分的成績，獲著名學府喬治城大學（Georgetown University）錄取。然而，在他打算申請助學金以應付首年2萬美元（約15.7萬港元）的學費時，被家人因其性取向而拒絕配合。由於歐文無法負擔昂貴學費，加上他在獲得錄取通知後，已回絕其他學府，故有如大學夢幻滅。<br />\n<br />\n曾經教歐文生物科的老師知悉情況後，在「GoFundMe」設立專頁，為歐文籌款，表示希望可以「將不可能變成可能」。截至今早（1日）11時許，已籌得近6.5萬美元，遠高於2萬美元的目標。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n呢啲老竇老母真係食塞米<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n個仔大個唔撚睬你真係唔好問點解<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e09fe22a5bb637712d3ef96670663f3a2a9c82c6","tid":763581,"uid":136994,"like":110,"dislike":1,"score":109,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-01T08:58:33.000Z","msg":"個仔都唔夠耶穌親啊陰公<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"12c2484c7f5441f2e1992597ac1fe236cd8bde51","tid":763581,"uid":20816,"like":64,"dislike":2,"score":62,"quote":{"pid":"e09fe22a5bb637712d3ef96670663f3a2a9c82c6","tid":763581,"uid":136994,"like":110,"dislike":1,"score":109,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-01T08:58:33.000Z","msg":"個仔都唔夠耶穌親啊陰公<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-08-01T09:01:10.000Z","msg":"「你們不要想，我來是叫地上太平；我來並不是叫地上太平，乃是叫地上動刀兵。因為我來是叫人與父親生疏，女兒與母親生疏，媳婦與婆婆生疏。人的仇敵就是自己家裡的人。」（馬太福音10：34-36）"},{"pid":"a143e4e4f1ba6838e1817d3b980fbee65c0ada14","tid":763581,"uid":99568,"like":9,"dislike":33,"score":-24,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-01T09:02:17.000Z","msg":"死基佬美國左膠死全家"},{"pid":"f678b42ed85683a9678b2da28a4e8e068c69a480","tid":763581,"uid":58303,"like":22,"dislike":2,"score":20,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-01T09:04:14.000Z","msg":"如果發生係香港應該會冇人籌錢比佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但網上就激烈討論"},{"pid":"4f1512a3ec0340f1fedb19a7e10397ba9ef893c2","tid":763581,"uid":42767,"like":20,"dislike":4,"score":16,"quote":{"pid":"12c2484c7f5441f2e1992597ac1fe236cd8bde51","tid":763581,"uid":20816,"like":64,"dislike":2,"score":62,"quote":{"pid":"e09fe22a5bb637712d3ef96670663f3a2a9c82c6","tid":763581,"uid":136994,"like":110,"dislike":1,"score":109,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-01T08:58:33.000Z","msg":"個仔都唔夠耶穌親啊陰公<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-08-01T09:01:10.000Z","msg":"「你們不要想，我來是叫地上太平；我來並不是叫地上太平，乃是叫地上動刀兵。因為我來是叫人與父親生疏，女兒與母親生疏，媳婦與婆婆生疏。人的仇敵就是自己家裡的人。」（馬太福音10：34-36）"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-01T09:04:32.000Z","msg":"耶教=邪教"},{"pid":"e38692be8de7e523e362677f823d4ccad11e3a01","tid":763581,"uid":20816,"like":1,"dislike